item.description:
Steely Dan

Steely Dan, with their sophisticated blend of jazz, rock, funk, blues, traditional pop and R&B have sculpted an eclectic body of work that defy all rock & roll conventions. Becker and Fagen will draw from their three-decade-plus catalog of signature hits and album favorites, all of uncompromising quality. The duo will be supported, as always, by their tight, sophisticated band of the world-class R&B and jazz players, so don't miss them when they come to your city.

Tickets start at 60.50 up to 120.50 depending on choice of seats.
